      <h1 class="display-4" style="text-align:center">How It Works</h1>

      <br>
    <div class="container" style="background-color:#e9ecef">
      <br>
        <div class="card-deck">
          <div class="card" style="width: 18rem; padding: 16px;" id="goal1">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="../resources/images/icon-step-1.png" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;width:50%;">
            <br><center>
            <h2 >Login to your account</h2>
            <br>
            <p>To post a listing for a found item, or to search for a lost item, you must create an account using your CU email. Then, login to the service to access these features.</p>
          </center>
          </div>

          <div class="card" style="width: 18rem; padding: 16px;" id="goal2">
              <img class="card-img-top" src="../resources/images/icon-step-2.png" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;width:50%;">
              <br><center>
              <h2 >Create a listing</h2>
              <br>
              <p>Create a listing for the found item and submit all of the details. If you need to, you may edit these details from your Account page.</p>
            </center>
          </div>

          <div class="card" style="width: 18rem; padding: 16px;" id="goal3">
              <img class="card-img-top" src="../resources/images/icon-step-3.png" style="margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;width:50%;">
              <br><center>
              <h2 >Let us do the work!</h2>
              <br>
              <p>Your listing will go live and be viewable to thousands of fellow Buff peers. If you lost an item, make sure to search for it regularly as newly found items are updated daily!
              </p>
            </center>
          </div>
          
      </div>
